艱<br />\n<br />\n所以，絕對唔需要否認自己係針對警隊，針對警隊就係對準政權。唔通你淨係針對林鄭、唔針對政制，就會有雙普選？<br />\n<br />\n#罷工罷巿罷買<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我參與全港三罷<br />\n#各區集會<br />\n#出核彈麻包袋都唔割蓆<br />\n#直至政府跪低<br />\n#抵制一切紅媒相關商業活動"},{"pid":"788dd0a053c49554e2d6c04141d9dff73d3bc6ab","tid":1445370,"uid":282054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:14:57.000Z","msg":"10連推"},{"pid":"15597c964e7b430df8c0db2cbd35f89944b90c70","tid":1445370,"uid":282054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:15:08.000Z","msg":"10連推"},{"pid":"44ac8fa4e9d5ec6a1a17b084aa3b3b7cbb5b5550","tid":1445370,"uid":282054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:15:18.000Z","msg":"10連推"},{"pid":"8e2caee58fee99701537f28f21271512880e8a0f","tid":1445370,"uid":97104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:15:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人真抵死, 企定定俾狗捉</span>"},{"pid":"3bac03f2a90bbc4abdbe78854190bd7b5059cf3c","tid":1445370,"uid":71071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:15:27.000Z","msg":"推，全部人都好危險"},{"pid":"1764ee253c07630abe54f94431c0c0d9b2dd018f","tid":1445370,"uid":282054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:15:28.000Z","msg":"10連推"},{"pid":"49295761fb1e3d9b844e83d108fcaa1827907023","tid":1445370,"uid":282054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e2caee58fee99701537f28f21271512880e8a0f","tid":1445370,"uid":97104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:15:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人真抵死, 企定定俾狗捉</span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:15:43.000Z","msg":"已block"},{"pid":"8fdfeba05443169fa1c0694fa86f3350fb09dd6a","tid":1445370,"uid":282054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:16:11.000Z","msg":"再推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今晚10點，和理非回合】<br />\n<br />\n22:00 集合3至5萬人發動集體檢舉「向香港警察致敬」專頁，5分鐘後重複檢舉一次<br />\n網頁：<a href=\"https://m.f